{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dfc8f9aa61","title":"金博文的右派言论","origin":"《高等学校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c0e219d343","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"dfc8f9aa61"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"9f52cf6080","name":"金博文"},{"id":"ae54e5173d","name":"东北林学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f414746dad","type":"title","text":"金博文的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dfc8f9aa61"},{"id":"c4ce83c342","type":"authors","text":"东北林学院金博文","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dfc8f9aa61"},{"id":"a3e15bd3d1","type":"paragraph","text":"我要是上前线就把枪掉过来打共产党，如果有机枪的话那就更好。共产党领导的各项运动是狐狸打狼两头堵。群众运动不免要犯错误，可是每次都是群众运动，并且事后都得纠偏。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dfc8f9aa61"},{"id":"4c4f74feed","type":"paragraph","text":"那些元帅们都是杀人的刽子手。王院长是土改干部，两手沾满鲜血的人，怎么能够领导这么大的学校？","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dfc8f9aa61"},{"id":"686c2dbfaf","type":"paragraph","text":"美国过去给大米白面吃是让我们当亡国奴，共产党让我们吃小米粥是建设社会主义。可是谁不知道大米白面好吃呢？","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dfc8f9aa61"},{"id":"80ef71fa8f","type":"paragraph","text":"解放军都是亡命之徒，不怕死的魔鬼。解放军不拿群众一针一线，可是牵老百姓的大牛。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dfc8f9aa61"},{"id":"0d69bec830","type":"paragraph","text":"解放军把国民党军官活剥皮，怎能说是优待俘虏呢？乡下转业军人乱七八糟，我经常跟他们打架。黄继光是上级给任务不完成不行逼死的。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dfc8f9aa61"}],"page":{"id":"a4e8f46bf9","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"dfc8f9aa61","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}